        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <date>16 January 1831</date>
                    <salute>My dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
                  <p>I send you Fumaria Vaillantii and two or three other things as make weights to render it worth carriage.</p>
                  <p>I know of no other recommendation of the grasses than that they have all been named by Prinius (?).</p>
                  <p>Very truly | John Lindley</p> 
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        
